  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your <strong>cauliflower</strong> into florets and the <strong>stem[s]</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>cauliflower</strong> <strong>florets</strong> and <strong>chopped stem[s]</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the dish in the oven for 10-15 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
