    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, remove the dish from the oven and mix the <strong>cheese</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> through the roasted cauliflower</p><p>Top the dish with the <strong>rolled</strong> <strong>pastry</strong>, brush with a little <strong>milk </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven for a further 20 min or until the pastry is puffed up, golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>cauliflower cheese pie</strong></p>",
