      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>Dijon</strong> <strong>mustard</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong>, 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 1 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 1/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>mustard dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and toss through the mustard dressing – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
